i vant your blood tell me a story about a time that you bled a bit more than you wanted to here's one of mine i was trimming the truly unruly hedges with an electric trimmer it was a repetative motion of swipe with the trimmer and pull the junk away with my left hand missed the order and hit my left index finger with the trimmer it cut deep bled like crazy and hurt like hell i yelled and threw the trimmer across the yard on my run for the kitchen sink scared the crud out of the little old lady next door on my way out the door i asked the old lady to tell my wife what happened when she got home and that i'd be at the er she told my wife that i'd cut my finger off it was bad stitches but not severed i have a cool little j shaped scar now and no feeling in the tip of that finger that's one of mine what's yours i have a boykin spaniel named jack one day i found a stray german shepard in the yard and we named chad we decided we would take him in as an outside dog because he and jack got along alright one day my bff and i were walking the dogs it was spring break two years ago so it was very hot we brought the dogs back into the yard we had been on the street and they were panting we didnt have the water bowls outside but we had some water in chad's pen so we walked the dogs in once we were in we shut the pen door behind us and unleashed the dogs chad went first and drank some water when he was done jack went for some water but i guess being a stray made chad defensive about everything he thought was his cause he attacked jack it was horrible chad bitjacks back and started swinging jack all around i was screaming at my bff who was like frozen by the door to go get my dad but she was like horrified i was afraid that my little jackie was gonna die i was screaming to god to let him live so i grabbed chad around the chest and pulled as hard as i could i figured jack would just run away but he decided he wanted to attack back he lunged at chad and tried to bite him but he got my left arm instead i felt it yea but it didnt really hurt right then because i was focused more on my emotions but i could tell it was his teeth and i was shocked so i let go of chad chad went back to throwing jack around but jacks teeth were still in my arm so they kinda dragged through only then did my bff go to get my dad and when he came running out chad just stopped attacking and was all loveable doggie again but i was furious at chad and kept screaming at him my arm was in horrible shape it was swollen black and blue and pouring blood everywhere steadily running off my arm from a cut about an inch deep i still have the scar and yes my dog lived The Shining (film) Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Shaggy dog story Sin City Teen Girl Squad Piccolo Junior Saga Tenshinhan The Inside Humphrey Bogart Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Futurama (TV series - season 5) Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Main characters of Fullmetal Alchemist Escape from New York Conspiracy (TNG episode) Professional wrestling holds Father's Day (Doctor Who) One Tree Hill (TV series) The Marshall Mathers LP Miss Saigon Dog RuneScape quests Rose (Doctor Who) Swimming Pok__mon Live! Blood (computer game) The Empty Child Episodes of Lost (Season 2) Kodocha Aerial (dance move) Fast bowling Invader Zim Drill bit Diving Professional wrestling throws Reservoir Dogs Characters of Lost StarCraft: Uprising First aid Tag Kain (Legacy of Kain) Blood on the Tracks Knife Pittsburgh Steelers The Subtle Knife Fancy Crane YuYu Hakusho EastEnders Blood Simple Late Night with Conan O'Brien Yu-Gi-Oh! anime and manga characters Salad Fingers Poker jargon Hip hop collaborations Professional wrestling attacks The Time Machine Swingout Cincinnati Bengals Milton H. Erickson Captain Thunderbolt Red Hot Chili Peppers Wyatt Earp Characters of Naruto Grandview, U.S.A. Kill Bill Muslim ibn Aqeel Baseball Xiaolin Showdown Columbine High School massacre Nico Robin The Lion, th